Smart Attendance Management System - Project Prompt
Project Overview
Build a comprehensive Smart Attendance Management System that tracks student attendance, manages academic records, and provides analytics. The system includes an attendance tracker module that manages student data with validation, persistence, and reporting capabilities.

Core Features
1. Student Management

Add students with roll number, name, and semester
Validate roll numbers (1-9999 range)
Validate semester (1-8 range)
Prevent duplicate student entries
Store student data persistently in JSON format

2. Attendance Tracking

Mark attendance for students (total lectures vs attended lectures)
Calculate attendance percentage per student
Validate attendance data (attended â‰¤ total, non-negative values)
Update attendance records dynamically

3. Academic Records

Enter and store student marks (0-100 range)
Validate marks before saving
Link marks with student records
Support for updating marks

4. Analytics & Reporting

Calculate class-wide average attendance
Calculate class-wide average marks
Generate total student count
Display summary statistics
Support for detailed student reports

5. Data Persistence

Save student data to JSON file
Load data on application startup
Auto-create data directory if missing
Handle data serialization/deserialization
